# Golden Fog Gate Skip

This skip refers to the golden fog leading to the [Duke's Archives](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/the-duke-s-archives); it allows the player to enter the Archives without having to place the [Lordvessel](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/lordvessel) at the [Firelink Altar](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/firelink-altar).\
\
There are two ways to perform this skip: one involves using a deathcam, while the other requires very precise movement on a ledge out of bounds.

## External resources

Out of bound method with bow tutorial (PTDE but works on remastered ) [https://youtu.be/7FyROZ5oumM](https://youtu.be/7FyROZ5oumM) by Maarionette on YouTube.\

Out of bound method without bow tutorial ( extremely difficult ) [https://youtu.be/DPO4f66wx24?list=PLgswmMvZsZ1UmUU_DYlzIMaSyqDYOv57r](https://youtu.be/DPO4f66wx24?list=PLgswmMvZsZ1UmUU_DYlzIMaSyqDYOv57r) by aeiou on YouTube.

Deathcam Method [https://youtu.be/iDJ5KM3d7GQ](https://youtu.be/iDJ5KM3d7GQ) by **つーさんですよ** on YouTube.
